author: The Current
description:
Join The Current's Morning Show in the Afternoon live from the State Fair
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

For the 2025 Minnesota State Fair, join Jill and Nil from The Current's Morning Show ... in the Afternoon! The Morning Show will broadcast live from the MPR booth near the corner of Judson and Nelson from Monday, Aug. 25, to Thursday, Aug. 28, each day from 3 to 7 p.m. Come watch the show live and in person, or tune in, use the free smartphone app, tell your smart speaker to play The Current, or stream at thecurrent.org.

(Extra points if you get the "Mean Girls" reference in the video)

Subscribe to our channel:
http://www.youtube.com/user/893TheCurrent?sub_confirmation=1  

Like/Follow:
https://www.facebook.com/TheCurrent/  
https://www.instagram.com/thecurrent/
